00:10:55.720 --> 00:10:57.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Haydi başka kapıya.

130
00:10:57.560 --> 00:10:59.280  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Provalara başlayacağız.

131
00:10:59.720 --> 00:11:01.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Yazılmayan oyunun provasına mı?

132
00:11:01.160 --> 00:11:03.040  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
On sayfa yazdım, temize çekmek lazım.

133
00:11:03.200 --> 00:11:04.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
On sayfa mı?

134
00:11:04.600 --> 00:11:05.800  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Sahi mi?

135
00:11:06.120 --> 00:11:07.800  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Tabii. Adı bile belli.

136
00:11:08.520 --> 00:11:09.760  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Neymiş adı?

137
00:11:10.440 --> 00:11:13.720  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Yani birkaç isim var aklımda.
Onlardan biri olacağı belli.

138
00:11:14.680 --> 00:11:16.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Anladım, Rüştü.

139
00:11:17.240 --> 00:11:18.840  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Daktilo, Muzaffer.

140
00:11:19.360 --> 00:11:21.160  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Daktilo.

141
00:11:23.040 --> 00:11:24.840  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gülüşmeler]

142
00:11:29.200 --> 00:11:31.760  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Ne diyeceğiz?
-Piyeste rol teklif edeceğiz.

143
00:11:31.920 --> 00:11:34.680  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Tam ona göre bir rol var.
Yani ben yazınca olacak.

144
00:11:39.520 --> 00:11:41.840  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[vals müziği çalıyor]

145
00:11:42.920 --> 00:11:44.320  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[hapşırır]

146
00:12:16.560 --> 00:12:17.640  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Merhabalar.

147
00:12:18.200 --> 00:12:21.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Merhaba.
-Biz, halkevinin tiyatro kolundayız da.

148
00:12:21.640 --> 00:12:23.680  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[öksürür] Bendeniz Şair Yazar Rüştü.

149
00:12:26.000 --> 00:12:28.960  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ne yapıyorsunuz? Haydi yürü! Yürü!

150
00:12:37.480 --> 00:12:38.560  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Rüştü.

151
00:12:38.880 --> 00:12:40.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gök gürlüyor]

152
00:12:45.360 --> 00:12:47.040  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
O kıza şiir yazılmaz.

153
00:12:47.960 --> 00:12:50.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Niye?
-Elini sıkmadı senin.

154
00:12:50.640 --> 00:12:52.280  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Korktu. Herkes gibi.

155
00:12:52.880 --> 00:12:54.240  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Herkes gibi olana şiir yazılır mı?

156
00:12:54.360 --> 00:12:55.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Yazılmaz mı?

157
00:12:57.400 --> 00:13:00.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Yazılır mı?
-Biz bir kıza şiir yazmayacağız ki.

158
00:13:00.360 --> 00:13:01.920  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Kız bizim bahanemiz.

159
00:13:02.480 --> 00:13:04.280  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Aşk, bahanesidir şiirin.

160
00:13:04.400 --> 00:13:06.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Nasıl?
-Fena değil.

161
00:13:08.160 --> 00:13:09.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Nasılsın, Rüştü?

162
00:13:09.680 --> 00:13:10.880  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Kalabalık.

163
00:13:12.360 --> 00:13:13.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Kan geldi mi?

164
00:13:14.240 --> 00:13:15.240  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Biraz.

165
00:13:16.800 --> 00:13:19.720  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Nasılsın, Muzaffer?
-İyiyim hocam, siz nasılsınız?

166
00:13:20.040 --> 00:13:21.680  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
İyiyim. Çok iyiyim.

167
00:13:22.680 --> 00:13:23.920  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hatta size

168
00:13:24.200 --> 00:13:26.080  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
daha da iyi bir şey getirdim.

169
00:13:26.480 --> 00:13:29.440  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-[şaşırarak] Çıktı mı?
-Kavga bile çıkardı.

170
00:13:29.760 --> 00:13:31.480  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Geç bile kaldı bu kavga.

171
00:13:31.960 --> 00:13:35.080  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Sonunda putları yıkıyoruz.
-Yenilerini yaparlar, merak etme.

172
00:13:35.280 --> 00:13:36.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Dur. Dur bir dakika.

173
00:13:36.720 --> 00:13:38.160  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Dur, bekle. Kitabın kapağını aç.

174
00:13:38.240 --> 00:13:40.240  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Kitabı aç.
-Kitabın kapağını aç.

175
00:13:40.400 --> 00:13:42.560  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Bak! Üçünün de ismini yazmışlar.

176
00:13:43.480 --> 00:13:45.320  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Tam üç ay hasta yattım

177
00:13:45.600 --> 00:13:47.920  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Kendimi bilmeden
Ve şehrin sokaklarını...

178
00:13:51.040 --> 00:13:52.360  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Rüştü öksürür] Su ver su.

179
00:13:56.400 --> 00:13:57.520  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Al.

180
00:14:02.880 --> 00:14:04.960  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[derin derin nefes alıp verir]

181
00:14:07.360 --> 00:14:08.640  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Yaslan arkana.

182
00:14:10.440 --> 00:14:12.880  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hasta adama şiir okutuyorsun, okusana sen.

183
00:14:20.480 --> 00:14:22.320  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Balıklar için deniz lazım

184
00:14:23.000 --> 00:14:25.240  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Sevişmek için işsiz olmak

185
00:14:26.120 --> 00:14:30.160  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Ve geceleri yatakta
Duymamak için tabanlarının sızısını

186
00:14:30.480 --> 00:14:32.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Zengin olmak lazım

187
00:14:33.720 --> 00:14:35.680  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Halbuki ıslık çalmak için

188
00:14:35.840 --> 00:14:37.080  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Bir şey lazım değil.

189
00:14:41.120 --> 00:14:43.240  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ne elbisesiymiş bu? Altın kaplama galiba.

190
00:14:43.320 --> 00:14:44.800  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Kumaşlar İstanbul'dan geliyor babacığım.

191
00:14:44.880 --> 00:14:46.640  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Bu paraya Halep'ten de getirebilirdik.

192
00:14:47.200 --> 00:14:48.520  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Biraz da dondurma alacağız, tabii.

193
00:14:49.360 --> 00:14:51.320  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Milletin içinde bir şey yemeyin sokakta.

194
00:14:51.400 --> 00:14:52.920  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Dondurma satılmıyor zaten ne zamandır.

195
00:14:53.120 --> 00:14:56.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Dondurma yok mu bu şehirde?
-[alaycı] "Dondurma yok mu bu şehirde?"

196
00:14:56.560 --> 00:14:57.680  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Millet yiyecek ekmek bulamazken

197
00:14:57.760 --> 00:14:59.800  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
dondurma yok diye ağlamayacaksın,
değil mi? Haydi.

198
00:14:59.880 --> 00:15:01.480  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Bu yüzden ağlayacak
insan değilim babacığım.

199
00:15:01.560 --> 00:15:02.960  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Aferin.
-Hoşça kalın, Zikri amca.

200
00:15:03.080 --> 00:15:05.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Ne güzel taklit yapıyorsun
babamın yanında.

201
00:15:07.320 --> 00:15:09.520  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Kitap satışları nasıl gidiyor Muzaffer?

202
00:15:12.440 --> 00:15:14.920  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Enteresan bir teklif aldım
leblebici Şehmuz'dan.

203
00:15:15.120 --> 00:15:16.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Nasıl?

204
00:15:17.120 --> 00:15:18.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Dedi ki...

205
00:15:19.480 --> 00:15:22.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[yerel ağızla] "Senin bu kitapların
hepsine 2,5 lira vereyim."

206
00:15:22.720 --> 00:15:24.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ne yapacakmış kitapları?

207
00:15:24.760 --> 00:15:26.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Külahlık yapacakmış.

208
00:15:28.080 --> 00:15:29.760  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Sen ne söyledin peki?

209
00:15:30.000 --> 00:15:31.360  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
"Şiir bu kardeşim." dedim.

210
00:15:31.600 --> 00:15:34.800  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
"Tamam işte. Leblebisi biten okur."
dedi bana.

211
00:15:35.880 --> 00:15:37.560  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Bence şahane bir fikir.

212
00:15:37.840 --> 00:15:40.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Evet hocam, fiyatta anlaşamadık. Yoksa...

213
00:15:40.640 --> 00:15:43.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Ben anlaşırım, ben bir uğrayayım.
Benim için uygun bir fiyat.

214
00:15:43.080 --> 00:15:44.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Hayırlı günler, hocam.
-İyi günler, hocam.

215
00:15:44.760 --> 00:15:45.960  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Merhaba, Ayşegül. Merhaba.

216
00:15:46.120 --> 00:15:48.680  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Kuzenim Suzan, İstanbul'dan geldi.
Bu sene bizim sınıfta okuyacak.

217
00:15:48.920 --> 00:15:50.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Öyle mi?
-Edebiyat öğretmenimiz

218
00:15:50.240 --> 00:15:52.160  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Behçet Necati bey.
-Merhaba, memnun oldum hocam.

219
00:15:52.520 --> 00:15:53.680  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Merhaba, hoş geldiniz.

220
00:15:55.520 --> 00:15:57.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Demek isteyince tokalaşabiliyorsunuz.

221
00:15:57.960 --> 00:15:59.040  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Efendim?

222
00:16:02.000 --> 00:16:04.240  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Niçin arkadaşımın elini sıkmadınız?

223
00:16:06.880 --> 00:16:08.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Şey... Ben...

224
00:16:08.920 --> 00:16:10.280  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Durumu nasıl?

225
00:16:12.520 --> 00:16:14.280  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hastanede.

226
00:16:16.120 --> 00:16:17.320  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Geçmiş olsun.

227
00:16:17.880 --> 00:16:20.360  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Kolay geçecek bir şey değil.

228
00:16:21.080 --> 00:16:22.440  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hocam, okulda görüşürüz.

229
00:16:22.600 --> 00:16:24.440  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-İyi günler, hocam.
-Görüşürüz çocuklar.

230
00:16:27.720 --> 00:16:28.520  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Bu kız mı?

231
00:16:30.760 --> 00:16:32.040  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Neden kötü davrandın?

232
00:16:32.120 --> 00:16:33.560  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
İnsanoğlu, hocam.

233
00:16:33.920 --> 00:16:35.520  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
İyi davranınca, çabuk unutuyor.

234
00:16:36.200 --> 00:16:37.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Görüşürüz.

235
00:16:50.600 --> 00:16:52.640  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[metal dövme sesleri]

236
00:16:52.840 --> 00:16:54.720  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Kolay gelsin.
-Eyvallah.

237
00:16:54.880 --> 00:16:57.720  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Battal abi çok merak ediyorum,
atlar bu yaptığın işten memnun mu?

238
00:16:58.320 --> 00:17:00.520  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Birinin bana ayakkabı çaktığını
düşünüyorum da...

239
00:17:01.920 --> 00:17:04.760  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Ne istiyorsun yine?
-Sipariş ettiğin kitabı getirdim.

240
00:17:05.839 --> 00:17:07.119  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Muzaffer. Sen niye anlamıyorsun ya?

241
00:17:07.400 --> 00:17:09.760  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Benim okuma yazmam yok.
-Olsun, belki çocuklar okur.

242
00:17:10.240 --> 00:17:11.960  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Fesuphanallah!

243
00:17:12.240 --> 00:17:13.560  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Kaç para bu?
-On para.

244
00:17:13.640 --> 00:17:16.359  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Ver şuna bir on para.
-Zaten bir on kalmıştı.

245
00:17:16.720 --> 00:17:17.680  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Haydi al git.
-Al kitabı...

246
00:17:17.880 --> 00:17:19.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
İstemez!

247
00:17:21.079 --> 00:17:23.119  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Bir şiirimde mutlaka adın geçecek.

248
00:17:23.760 --> 00:17:26.560  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Okuma yazması yoktu ama
şiirin kıymetini biliyordu diye.

249
00:17:26.839 --> 00:17:28.119  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Baba ne satıyor bu?

250
00:17:28.400 --> 00:17:29.720  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Şiir.
-Şiir mi?

251
00:17:30.000 --> 00:17:30.800  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hakikaten mi?

252
00:17:31.040 --> 00:17:32.360  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-İster misin bir tane?
-İsterim.

253
00:17:32.480 --> 00:17:33.840  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Oku hele bir tane.
-Yok,

254
00:17:33.960 --> 00:17:34.840  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
kitap ister misin yani.

255
00:17:35.400 --> 00:17:37.440  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Canım bir tadına bakalım,
beğenirsek alırız.

256
00:17:38.360 --> 00:17:41.800  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Madem öyle, kitaptan
rastgele bir sayfa açıyorum

257
00:17:42.080 --> 00:17:44.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ve abimin şansınadır diye okuyorum.

258
00:17:44.560 --> 00:17:46.560  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Şiirin ismi "Ölüler Konuşuyor."

259
00:17:47.480 --> 00:17:49.240  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Dünyaya bir daha gelirsem

