00:25:34.520 --> 00:25:37.160  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Çizgi, yazdın mı?
-Yazdık, çizgiyi de yazdık.

394
00:25:37.800 --> 00:25:39.560  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
