Ben ma...

396
00:25:41.280 --> 00:25:44.280  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Yahu görmüyorum! Şuraya tutacaksın.
-Bir yaz kardeşim, boş ver.

397
00:25:44.480 --> 00:25:46.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Göstereyim sana.
Şöyle tutacaksın. Seyret...

398
00:25:59.640 --> 00:26:01.560  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Güle güle, Muzaffer bey.

399
00:26:29.440 --> 00:26:31.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Aynayı getir.

400
00:26:48.760 --> 00:26:51.080  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Bir erkek evladın olduğunda

401
00:26:52.040 --> 00:26:54.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
kendini daha emniyette hisseder insan.

402
00:26:55.280 --> 00:26:56.280  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Der ki,

403
00:26:56.800 --> 00:26:59.920  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
"Tamam artık. Yalnız değilim bu savaşta.

404
00:27:00.200 --> 00:27:02.080  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Bir de oğlum olacak yanımda.

405
00:27:02.840 --> 00:27:05.520  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Benim yapamadığım her şeyi o yapacak."

406
00:27:07.200 --> 00:27:08.240  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ben,

407
00:27:08.680 --> 00:27:11.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
