götüremedim bu gemiyi.

408
00:27:12.840 --> 00:27:14.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ama oğlum,

409
00:27:14.240 --> 00:27:15.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
deryaları aşacak.

410
00:27:16.160 --> 00:27:17.840  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[bağırarak] Doğru tut!

411
00:27:22.800 --> 00:27:24.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Sonra...

412
00:27:27.280 --> 00:27:31.240  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
...oğlum azmin değil,
bir hevesin peşine düşer

413
00:27:32.800 --> 00:27:34.280  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ve her şey biter.

414
00:27:49.680 --> 00:27:51.760  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ya, üzgünüm ya işte Muzaffer.

415
00:27:53.280 --> 00:27:55.040  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Kovuldum diye
seni mi teselli edeyim Rüştü?

416
00:27:55.280 --> 00:27:56.760  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Birazcık yardımcı olabilirsin.

417
00:27:57.120 --> 00:27:59.240  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Yani suçlu hissediyorum işte kendimi.

418
00:28:00.560 --> 00:28:02.080  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[öksürür ve zor konuşur]
Suçlusun zaten Rüştü.

419
00:28:03.440 --> 00:28:04.840  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Bir de iyi tarafından bak.

420
00:28:04.960 --> 00:28:08.560  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Ben raporluyum, sen kovuldun.
