422
00:28:11.160 --> 00:28:13.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
İyimser mi daha cesur, kötümser mi?

423
00:28:50.840 --> 00:28:52.160  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Bravo, Suzan.

424
00:28:58.120 --> 00:28:59.640  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
