464
00:30:36.640 --> 00:30:40.960  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Merak etme, ben kendi başımın
çaresine bakabilirim Kürşat bey.

465
00:31:00.880 --> 00:31:01.960  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Yılanlar!

466
00:31:02.440 --> 00:31:04.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
