491
00:32:35.840 --> 00:32:37.040  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Mehmet!

492
00:32:37.160 --> 00:32:38.240  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Suzan] Mehmet!

493
00:32:38.320 --> 00:32:39.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Suzan!

494
00:32:39.480 --> 00:32:41.440  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Hatice!
-Mehmet!

495
00:32:51.000 --> 00:32:52.280  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hayırdır, çocuklar?

496
00:32:57.960 --> 00:33:00.880  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Çocuklar, ben size benden daktiloyu
hiçbir zaman istemeyin demedim mi?

497
00:33:01.120 --> 00:33:02.320  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hep söylediğiniz şey hocam.

498
00:33:02.520 --> 00:33:04.480  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hâlâ nasıl istiyoruz, ben de anlamıyorum.

499
00:33:04.720 --> 00:33:07.280  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Okulun daktilosu. Beni de kovdurmayın da.

500
00:33:07.720 --> 00:33:09.560  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Yarın öğlen burada olacak.
-Yarın mı?

501
00:33:09.640 --> 00:33:10.760  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Evet, Rüştü. Yarın.

502
00:33:11.000 --> 00:33:13.240  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
