-Sağ olun hocam.

514
00:33:39.840 --> 00:33:41.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Hocam...
-Ne?

515
00:33:43.040 --> 00:33:45.160  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Bizim yazacak yerimiz de yok.

516
00:33:48.800 --> 00:33:51.680  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
