Sağ ol.

655
00:45:41.480 --> 00:45:42.640  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Şey, bak

656
00:45:42.840 --> 00:45:45.480  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
bu zarfı senin için getirdim.
Bunun içinde iki tane şiir var.

657
00:45:45.640 --> 00:45:47.280  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Bir bakarsan...
-Suzan!

658
00:45:47.720 --> 00:45:50.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Ne yapıyorsun?
-Geliyorum, Kürşat.

659
00:45:51.480 --> 00:45:54.520  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Konuşuyoruz, görmüyor musun?
-Konuşuyorsun da

660
00:45:54.680 --> 00:45:56.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
senin ağzından çıkacak bir mikrop

661
00:45:56.720 --> 00:45:59.680  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
bu kızı çok hasta edebilir,
bunun farkında mısın?

662
00:45:59.920 --> 00:46:02.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Bence, bu pislik söyledi babana.

663
00:46:02.520 --> 00:46:03.760  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Bana pislik mi dedin sen?

664
00:46:04.000 --> 00:46:05.520  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Evet. Sen...

665
00:46:05.600 --> 00:46:07.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Sen bana pislik mi dedin?
-Kürşat!

666
00:46:07.200 --> 00:46:08.480  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Bana pislik mi dedin?

667
00:46:08.560 --> 00:46:09.800  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Pislik!
-Sen kimsin lan!

668
00:46:09.880 --> 00:46:11.760  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Her yerde karşıma çıkıyorsun lan!
-Kürşat!

669
00:46:11.880 --> 00:46:12.800  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Kimsin!
-İmdat!

670
00:46:12.880 --> 00:46:14.080  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Çocuklar!

671
00:46:22.320 --> 00:46:23.960  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Haydi Suzan, yürü ya.

672
00:46:27.200 --> 00:46:28.560  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Yukarı.

673
00:46:30.200 --> 00:46:32.320  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[yağmur sesleri]

674
00:46:32.720 --> 00:46:36.240  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Düğün, bayram... Bunlar
kavga etmek için ideal zamanlardır.

675
00:46:37.040 --> 00:46:38.280  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Bence de.

676
00:46:38.680 --> 00:46:41.920  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ama bir dahakine yaşıtlarını seç bence.

677
00:46:43.160 --> 00:46:45.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Neyse ki altı kişiydiler.

678
00:46:45.440 --> 00:46:46.960  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Neyse ki.

679
00:46:50.280 --> 00:46:51.520  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
İyi misin?

680
00:46:54.440 --> 00:46:56.280  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
İyi bayramlar Muzaffer Bey.

681
00:46:57.560 --> 00:46:59.160  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
İyi bayramlar hocam.

682
00:47:13.640 --> 00:47:16.760  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Gözler neler eyler
Neler işrap

683
00:47:18.080 --> 00:47:20.160  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Uçmakta bu ateşli havada

684
00:47:20.360 --> 00:47:23.680  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Vuslat demi
Bir kuş gibi bitap

685
00:47:23.880 --> 00:47:26.040  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Vuslat. Vuslat nedir, Şahin?

686
00:47:26.400 --> 00:47:28.080  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Nasıl hocam? [sınıfta gülüşmeler]

687
00:47:28.360 --> 00:47:29.880  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Oturabilirsin Şahin.

688
00:47:30.400 --> 00:47:32.080  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Vuslat nedir Ayşegül?

689
00:47:32.200 --> 00:47:33.480  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Kavuşmak, hocam.

690
00:47:34.040 --> 00:47:36.880  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Aferin. Neymiş? Kavuşmak.

691
00:47:37.480 --> 00:47:38.920  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Vuslat.

692
00:47:40.320 --> 00:47:43.640  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Vuslat... demi.

693
00:47:44.520 --> 00:47:45.840  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Dem nedir?

694
00:47:46.320 --> 00:47:47.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Zaman hocam.

695
00:47:47.600 --> 00:47:49.480  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Zaman, an. Aferin, Kürşat.

696
00:47:50.800 --> 00:47:53.280  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Vuslat demi, yani kavuşma anı,

697
00:47:53.480 --> 00:47:55.280  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
bir kuş gibi bitap.

698
00:47:55.440 --> 00:47:57.240  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Bu kuş neden bitap, Şahin?

699
00:47:57.760 --> 00:47:59.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Çok uçmuş olabilir hocam.

700
00:48:00.840 --> 00:48:03.520  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Edebiyattan anlamıyor ama
kuşlardan gayet güzel anlıyor.

701
00:48:03.680 --> 00:48:04.800  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Aferin Şahin.

702
00:48:05.040 --> 00:48:06.920  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Tarihinde ilk defa bir soruyu bildin,
biliyor musun?

703
00:48:07.040 --> 00:48:08.840  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Girin.

704
00:48:09.520 --> 00:48:12.360  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Hocam, Suzan Özsoy arkadaşımızı
müdüriyetten çağırıyorlar.

705
00:48:12.520 --> 00:48:13.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Öyle mi?

706
00:48:13.720 --> 00:48:15.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Buyurun Suzan Hanım.
Sizin için de değişiklik olur.

707
00:48:15.480 --> 00:48:17.280  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Uykunuz açılır.

708
00:48:23.400 --> 00:48:26.520  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Vuslat demi
Bir kuş gibi bitap

709
00:48:27.520 --> 00:48:29.360  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hani müdüriyete gidiyorduk?

710
00:48:39.600 --> 00:48:42.080  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Sağ ol Veli.
Hatırlat, sonra sana kitabımı vereceğim.

711
00:48:42.160 --> 00:48:43.560  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Sağ ol abi, vermiştin.

712
00:48:45.320 --> 00:48:46.920  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Sevgilin olunca, ona verirsin.

713
00:48:47.040 --> 00:48:48.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ona verdim zaten abi.

714
00:48:49.520 --> 00:48:51.520  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Tamam Veli, gidebilirsin.

715
00:48:53.120 --> 00:48:54.680  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Sen ne yapıyorsun burada?

716
00:48:55.240 --> 00:48:56.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Yarın okul çıkışı

717
00:48:57.040 --> 00:48:59.240  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
sahilde buluşalım mı seninle?

718
00:49:00.880 --> 00:49:02.320  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Bilmiyorum.

719
00:49:02.440 --> 00:49:04.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ben seni bekleyeceğim.

720
00:49:05.480 --> 00:49:07.320  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Haydi git artık.
-Ben seni bekleyeceğim Suzan.

721
00:49:07.640 --> 00:49:09.080  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Git.
-Bak, Suzan.

722
00:49:09.240 --> 00:49:12.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Suzan! Sen gelmesen bile,
ben seni beklemeye devam edeceğim.

723
00:49:12.080 --> 00:49:13.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Muzaffer, git.
-Bekleyeceğim!

724
00:49:13.200 --> 00:49:14.240  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Gider misin?
-Bekleyeceğim seni.

725
00:49:14.320 --> 00:49:15.960  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Senelerce bekleyeceğim.
-Lütfen git.

726
00:49:16.160 --> 00:49:17.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Bekleyeceğim.
-Çabuk git!

727
00:49:17.400 --> 00:49:19.320  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hayır, ben buradayım, sen git. Suzan!

728
00:49:19.520 --> 00:49:21.680  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Suzan, bekleyeceğim seni.

729
00:49:23.200 --> 00:49:24.440  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Suzan!

730
00:49:25.760 --> 00:49:27.680  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
"Ben çok iyiyim kardeşim.

731
00:49:27.800 --> 00:49:30.280  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
İlaçlar, tedavi. Her şey mükemmel.

732
00:49:30.760 --> 00:49:33.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Meğer üç öğün yemek yeyince
iyileşiyormuş insan.

733
00:49:34.120 --> 00:49:36.080  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Neyse, fazla yazmayayım orasını.

734
00:49:36.640 --> 00:49:39.960  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Sıkı dur... Burada bir kızla tanıştım.

735
00:49:40.680 --> 00:49:43.920  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Yani bu mektubu yazar yazmaz
gidip tanışacağım.

736
00:49:44.880 --> 00:49:46.840  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Şu anda bana bakıyor kendisi.

737
00:49:48.040 --> 00:49:50.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Buradakilerle senin meseleni konuştum.

738
00:49:50.560 --> 00:49:53.360  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Menfi cevap verdiler ama ben
onların seviyesine inmedim.

739
00:49:53.720 --> 00:49:57.280  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>Sıra mıra diyorlar ama</i>
<i>kafalarını şişirmeye devam ediyorum.</i>

740
00:49:57.640 --> 00:50:00.080  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>Sen neler yapıyorsun, üstat? İyi misin?</i>

741
00:50:01.080 --> 00:50:03.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>Suzan'a şiirleri verdin mi?</i>

742
00:50:03.360 --> 00:50:04.920  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>Hangisini beğendi?</i>

743
00:50:05.320 --> 00:50:06.920  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>Neden yazmıyorsun?</i>

744
00:50:07.200 --> 00:50:09.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>Bana yazacak tek bir satır</i>
<i>yaşamadın mı be adam?"</i>

745
00:50:09.240 --> 00:50:10.480  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Merhaba.

746
00:50:15.360 --> 00:50:16.880  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Neydi o?

747
00:50:19.120 --> 00:50:20.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Rüştü'nün mektubu.

748
00:50:20.560 --> 00:50:22.520  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ya? İyi miymiş peki?

749
00:50:22.800 --> 00:50:25.920  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
İyiymiş, keyfi yerinde.
Birisiyle tanıştım diyor. Yani,

750
00:50:26.120 --> 00:50:28.720  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-tanışmak üzere.
-Yok canım, kimmiş?

751
00:50:29.560 --> 00:50:32.080  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Bilmiyorum, uçtu gitti.

752
00:50:32.480 --> 00:50:34.640  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gülüşürler]

753
00:50:37.800 --> 00:50:39.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Şiir verecektin.

754
00:50:40.560 --> 00:50:42.480  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Onun için mi geldin?
-Hıhı.

755
00:50:42.840 --> 00:50:43.960  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Yanımda değil.

756
00:50:44.040 --> 00:50:46.040  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Aklında değil mi? Okusana.

757
00:50:47.800 --> 00:50:49.800  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Okuyup, hangisini beğendiğini
sen söyleyeceksin.

758
00:50:52.320 --> 00:50:54.840  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Tam da Hatice madene gidecekti.

759
00:50:55.720 --> 00:50:58.360  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Ne?
-Mükellefiyet zamanında yani.

760
00:50:58.440 --> 00:51:01.320  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Gerçek hayatta değil. Oyunda yani.

761
00:51:01.640 --> 00:51:03.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Anladım.
-Yoksa böyle bir şey,

762
00:51:03.200 --> 00:51:05.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
mümkün değil, öyle değil mi?

763
00:51:05.200 --> 00:51:09.080  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Sen delirmiyorsun, değil mi?
-Kılık değiştirsek, Hatice gibi?

764
00:51:10.640 --> 00:51:12.080  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Unut bunu.

765
00:51:13.040 --> 00:51:14.280  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Çok tehlikeli.

766
00:51:14.800 --> 00:51:16.160  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Mahvederler bizi.

767
00:51:17.040 --> 00:51:18.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Yazık.

768
00:51:19.440 --> 00:51:22.800  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Beni oraya götürecek
başka birini bulurum o zaman.

769
00:51:24.640 --> 00:51:26.760  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Seni oraya baban götürsün.

770
00:51:33.720 --> 00:51:35.880  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Artık gitmeliyim. Ayşegül bekliyor.

771
00:51:36.080 --> 00:51:37.520  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Dur.

772
00:51:38.400 --> 00:51:40.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Gene buluşacak mıyız?

773
00:51:42.480 --> 00:51:45.320  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Çok tehlikeli. Mahvederler bizi.

774
00:52:19.480 --> 00:52:21.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Suzan! Suzan!

775
00:52:22.360 --> 00:52:23.520  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Merhaba.
-Merhaba.

776
00:52:30.520 --> 00:52:32.080  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
İşte şiirler.

777
00:52:36.480 --> 00:52:38.480  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Bunlar da kıyafetlerimiz.

778
00:52:40.000 --> 00:52:41.640  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hatice gibi.

779
00:52:42.720 --> 00:52:44.360  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Şimdi mi?

780
00:52:44.640 --> 00:52:45.840  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Haydi çabuk.

781
00:52:46.080 --> 00:52:47.080  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Tamam.

782
00:52:47.640 --> 00:52:50.440  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Ayşegül bunları alır mısın?
-Suzan, nereye gidiyorsun?

783
00:52:50.520 --> 00:52:52.720  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
İki saat sonra sizdeyim,
merak etmeyin, tamam mı?

784
00:52:54.840 --> 00:52:57.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Haydi.

785
00:53:02.120 --> 00:53:03.720  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
O kadar beyazsın ki hemen yakalanacağız.

786
00:53:03.800 --> 00:53:06.480  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Sanki sen değilsin.
